aign=editorial&ns_source=twitter&ns_mchannel=reseaux_sociaux&ns_fee=0&ns_linkname=node_843168 |date=20131028132432 }}</ref><ref>CNN (in arabic)Egypt: Investigation into an Israeli scheme caught with a participant of Black Bloc http://arabic.cnn.com/2013/middle_east/1/31/egypt.blackblock/index.html {{Wayback|url=http://arabic.cnn.com/2013/middle_east/1/31/egypt.blackblock/index.html |date=20131212173148 }}</ref>一群年轻的抗议者，称自己为“黑块”，通过阻断亚历山大港电车轨道的行为而在埃及革命两周年纪念这天留下了永久的痕迹。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/63247/Egypt/Politics-/%E2%80%98Black-Bloc%E2%80%99-stops-tramway-in-Alexandria,-protests.aspx|script-title=en:‘Black Bloc’ stops tramway in Alexandria, protests in Cairo|publisher=Ahram Online|accessdate=Aug 26, 2013|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225060324/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/63247/Egypt/Politics-/%E2%80%98Black-Bloc%E2%80%99-stops-tramway-in-Alexandria,-protests.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContentP/1/63243/Egypt/Live-Updates-Protests,-clashes-all-over-the-countr.aspx|title=Live Updates 1: Protests, clashes all over the country on revolution's anniversary|publisher=Ahram Online|accessdate=Aug 26, 2013|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120144310/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContentP/1/63243/Egypt/Live-Updates-Protests,-clashes-all-over-the-countr.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-21228852|title=Black Bloc anarchists emerge|date=28 January 2013|publisher=BBC News|access-date=2013-11-07|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002302/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-21228852|dead-url=no}}</ref>埃及总检察长塔拉特·阿卜杜拉下令警察和武装部队逮捕任何的黑块参与者，并且指出这个群体开展“恐怖活动”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.news24.com/Africa/News/Egypts-Black-Bloc-in-govt-crosshairs-20130201|title=Egypt's Black Bloc in govt crosshairs|publisher=News24|accessdate=Aug 26, 2013|a